# ==================== KEEP THESE FILES ====================
# These are tracked and should be uploaded to GitHub:
#
# ✅ pom.xml                    - Maven build file
# ✅ README.md                  - Documentation
# ✅ LICENSE                    - License file
# ✅ src/                       - Source code
# ✅ xmpp-bridge/index.js       - XMPP bridge source
# ✅ xmpp-bridge/package.json   - Node dependencies
# ✅ xmpp-bridge/README.md      - Bridge documentation
# ✅ dino-game/                 - Easter egg (if you want to keep it)
#
# ❌ EXCLUDED (download separately or build from source):
# ❌ valvoice-xmpp.exe          - Build with: cd xmpp-bridge && npm run build:exe
# ❌ SoundVolumeView.exe        - Download from: https://www.nirsoft.net/utils/sound_volume_view.html
# ❌ PowerShell/                - Bundled runtime (too large)
